{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fb6029a4c7","title":"视察安徽时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aa5c5b2907","index":0,"year":1958,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"fb6029a4c7","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0eb8f76b2c","type":"title","text":"视察安徽时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"44be075b64","type":"paragraph","text":"（对钢铁工业的指示）（一九五八年九月二十日）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c31a21cd0f","type":"paragraph","text":"发展钢铁事业，一定要搞群众运动，什么工作都要群众运动，不搞群众运动是不行的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03b6f31568","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c31c99c0b","type":"paragraph","text":"马鞍山条件很好，可以发展成为中型钢铁联合企业，因为发展中型的钢铁联合企业比较快。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2c59e75764","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8acc3559b3","type":"paragraph","text":"劳动人民万岁！劳动人民万岁！","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7be59a46df","type":"paragraph","text":"（视察舒茶公社时的谈话）（一九五八年九月廿四日）","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e521060369","type":"paragraph","text":"吃饭不要钱，既然一个社能办到，其他有条件的社也能办到。既然吃饭可以不要钱，将来穿衣服也可以不要钱了。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea92e6e84e","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ff3ca0b03","type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社将来要集中种蔬菜，种蔬菜也要专业化。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4aaaf32ec9","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"095ccbb0a3","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛主席在参现除四害陈列馆时说）老鼠这个东西很狡猾，这样，老鼠就要大遭殃啦！","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"abbdcbe495","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6e526f24c","type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，人民公社好。","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2afb944da1","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a8dca8764","type":"paragraph","text":"......以后山坡上要多开辟茶园。（视察合肥时的谈话）（一九五八年九月）","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e6d8f4abc","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛主席到合肥时高兴地说）沿途一望，生气勃勃，肯定是有希望的，有大希望的。","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffb51658ec","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛主席在与妇女干部谈话时说）如果每年每人没有一千，。两千斤粮食，没有公共食堂，没有幸厢院托儿所，没有扫除文盲，没有进小学，中学，大学，妇女还不可能彻底解放。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a163daa4cd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席指出，只有办好人民公社，才是妇女彻底解放的道路。","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"fb6029a4c7","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":255,"end":254}}}},"__N_SSG":true}